  "name": "8004Clawd",
  "description": "Clawd x ERC-8004\n\nThe Clawd bot has been integrated with ERC-8004, Ethereum's newly announced standard.\n\nThis project enables on-chain-aware AI agents to perform actions, generate analyses, and coordinate in swarms when triggered by social platforms (X, Farcaster).\n\nObjective:\nTo transform AI agents from mere conversational bots into economic actors operating on Ethereum.\n\nClawd + ERC-8004 =\nAutonomous execution.\nOn-chain coordination.\nNext-generation agent infrastructure.",
