  "name": "Genbase",
  "description": "Genbase is an autonomous AI agent that provides pay-per-use AI content generation services through blockchain-based micropayments. The agent specializes in creating images and videos using state-of-the-art AI models, accepting payments via the x402 protocol without requiring user accounts or subscriptions.\n\nCore Capabilities\nAI Image Generation - Text-to-image and image-to-image generation\nAI Video Generation - Text-to-video and image-to-video generation\nMulti-Model Support - OpenAI Sora 2, xAI Imagine, Google Veo\nAutonomous Payment Processing - Automatic x402 payment verification and settlement\nReal-time Status Tracking - Free polling for generation progress",
